./fix-l1-lock.yaml:11:    task_instruction: "Implement fcntl.flock-based locking per prd/PRD.md. Modify src/unison/lock.py only. Add import fcntl. acquire() uses os.open + fcntl.flock(LOCK_EX|LOCK_NB). release() uses fcntl.flock(LOCK_UN) + os.close + unlink. is_locked() probes with a test fd. Fall back to existing PID-file logic if fcntl unavailable or EAGAIN. Add test_concurrent_acquire to tests/test_lock.py. pytest tests/test_lock.py -q must pass (16+). git add -A && git commit."
